posting_body: ['Text', 'show contact info', 'to setup a showing!', 'AREA:', 'Centennial / Fairways of South Suburban', 'FEATURES:', 'Brand new full renovation!', 'High end granite countertops, new kitchen appliances, new carpet, new paint and more.', 'Pool access.', 'INCLUDED UTILITIES:', 'N/A', 'TENANT PAID UTILITIES:', 'All utilities are paid by the tenant.', 'BEDROOMS & BATHROOMS: 5 bedrooms 3.5 bathrooms.', 'KITCHEN APPLIANCES INCLUDED: All new refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, garbage disposal.', 'LAUNDRY:', 'Washer/dryer included.', 'FLOORING: Hardwood and carpet.', 'HEAT/COOLING: Central heat and AC.', 'PARKING: 3 car attached garage.', 'FENCING: Fully fenced.', 'BASEMENT: Finished basement.', 'RESTRICTIONS: Pets are considered with a one-time non-refundable pet fee of $250 per pet.', 'Sorry, but we cannot allow any of the following breeds of dog: American Pit Bull Terrier, American Staffordshire Terrier, and Staffordshire Bull Terrier.', 'SECURITY DEPOSIT:', "The security deposit is equal to one month's rent.", 'APPLICATION FEE: $30 per adult.', 'Please note we have a 700 minimum credit score for all properties.', 'AVAILABILITY DATE: Today!', "**Applicants must be able to start a lease within 1 week of the property's listed availability date.", '**', 'LEASE TERM: Initial lease to end April through June of 2023 with 12 month extensions possible at that time', 'Growing marijuana inside or outside the premises is not allowed, smoking of any kind inside the property is not allowed.', 'Minimum 700 credit score required.']
